    <abstract>
      <t>   This document provides a specification of the Network Function
   Virtualization (NFV) YANG service model.  The NFV service module
   serves as a base framework for managing an universal Customer-
   Premises Equipment (uCPE) NFV subsystem from the Orchestrator.

